OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FGrenfell's legacy: Should I
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F'stay put' if there's a    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ffire in my tower block?    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, As Grenfell Tower burned, residents    
OL,6, were told to stay in their flats and 72
OL,7, people died. Five years on, "stay put" 
OL,8, remains the policy for fires in most   
OL,9, high-rise buildings. But the government
OL,10, is now facing a legal challenge after  
OL,11, deciding it is not practical to provide
OL,12, personal escape plans for disabled     
OL,13, residents.                             
OL,15,FIn the early hours of 14 June 2017 on  
OL,16,Fthe 9th floor of Grenfell Tower, Hanan 
OL,17,FWahabi's 16-year-old son Zak made a    
OL,18,Fcrucial decision. The building had a   
OL,19,Fpolicy - to "stay put" if there was a  
OL,20,Ffire.                                  
